timing_library...om_timing_arcs(25.10)  timing_library...om_timing_arcs(25.10)

Name
       timing_library_infer_async_pins_from_timing_arcs

Syntax
       timing_library_infer_async_pins_from_timing_arcs

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       When set to true, a pin is marked clear if it has timing arcs with type
       "clear"  to  output  pins.  The  sequential block is not required to be
       present in the cell for marking a pin as clear.

       To set this global variable, use the set_global command.

